{"id":706,"date":"2021-01-14T09:32:27","date_gmt":"2021-01-14T08:32:27","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.gotriple.eu\/?page_id=706"},"modified":"2022-04-04T13:18:00","modified_gmt":"2022-04-04T11:18:00","slug":"participate-in-the-co-design-workshops","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/participate-in-the-co-design-workshops\/","title":{"rendered":"Co-Design Workshops"},"content":{"rendered":"<div id=\"modal-ready\">\n<p><a href=\"#List-of-Upcoming-Workshops\"><strong>List of Upcoming Workshops<\/strong><\/a><br><strong><a href=\"#List-of-Past-Workshops\">List of Past Workshops<\/a><\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-text-color has-background is-style-wide\" style=\"background-color:#622166;color:#622166\"\/>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Participate in the Co-Design Workshops and help us shape the GoTriple platform!<\/strong><br><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Our team is planning some co-design workshops where potential users of the platform will be directly and actively involved in the design of GoTriple . The most effective way to design a platform or application is to listen to real users, that&#8217;s why <strong>you&#8217;re invited<\/strong> to take part in the design process and participate in the workshops.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Each worksop will focus on a specific functionality or page of the platform. Workshops will be held remotely (using Zoom, Teams or Google Meet) and will last between <strong>two and three hours<\/strong>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p id=\"List-of-Upcoming-Workshops\">If you&#8217;d like to participate, simply send an email to the respective workshop organiser that you find in the description of the workshops below.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"List-of-Upcoming-Workshops\">List of Upcoming Workshops<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<h4>GoTriple Trust Building System (TBS)<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>The Trust Building System of GoTriple will be used to detect reliable partners for SSH researchers. The TBS can be applied to a vast array of applications such as interdisciplinary collaboration, funding opportunities and partnerships, and would help to provide win-win situation for all stakeholders within and outside the SSH community.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>An early prototype of the TBS is ready to be tested and improved by your input. To test it, all you need is to have a real request to solve, and if you think your private network or their trusted peers could help you solve it.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\ud83d\uddd3 Date: <strong>Everyday<\/strong><br>\ud83d\ude4b\u200d\u2640\ufe0f <strong>TO PARTICIPATE<\/strong>: send an email to <a href=\"mailto:maxime.bouillard@meoh.io\">maxime.bouillard@meoh.io<\/a> or <a href=\"mailto:gael@meoh.io\">gael@meoh.io<\/a> and we will invite you to the TBS! We cannot wait to see you there!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:70px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"List-of-Past-Workshops\">List of Past Workshops<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<h4>Search Results Page Workshop<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>The GoTriple platform will be an innovative discovery platform.&nbsp;Help us design the search results page by participating in our workshop. Make sure what\u2019s important to you is displayed on the page and in the way you\u2019d like to see the information and metrics of the search results.&nbsp;<br><br>\ud83d\uddd3 Date: <strong>Wed 14th July at 11.00 CEST (1 hour)<\/strong><br>\ud83d\ude4b\u200d\u2640\ufe0f <strong>TO PARTICIPATE<\/strong>: please contact&nbsp;<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"mailto:p.forbes@abertay.ac.uk\" target=\"_blank\">p.forbes@abertay.ac.uk<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"\/>\n\n\n\n<h4>MyGoTriple Page Workshop<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>The private user dashboard (called \u201cMyGoTriple\u201d) will be your personal page on GoTriple: here you will find all the relevant information related to your activity on the platform. Help us design the MyGoTriple page, defining what is important to display and how to display all the relevant information.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\ud83d\uddd3  Date: <strong>Wed 7th July at 11.00 CEST<\/strong> (1 hour)<\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"\/>\n\n\n\n<h4>Disciplines Dashboard Workshop<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>The wide range of social sciences and humanities disciplines will be at the center of the GoTriple user experience and this dashboard is where all the disciplines will be available. Help us understand the importance of disciplines and how to present them on this page.<br>This workshop will be held by Giulio Andreini of Net7 Srl.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\ud83d\uddd3  Date: <strong>13th of June 2021 at 14.30 CEST<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"\/>\n\n\n\n<h4>GoTriple Dashboard Workshop<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>The general dashboard of GoTriple will be used to provide interesting information about the whole platform. Help us understand how this page will be useful for the GoTriple users and what we should display on this page.<br>This workshop will be held by Giulio Andreini of Net7 Srl.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\ud83d\uddd3  Date: <strong>8th June 2021, 14:30 CEST<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"\/>\n\n\n\n<h4>MyGoTriple : Annotation Tool<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>here you will find all the relevant information related to your activity on the platform. Help us design the MyGoTriple annotation tool, tell us what is important to you when highlighting and commenting on textual material.<br>This workshop was held by Paula Forbes of Abertay University.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\ud83d\uddd3 Date: <strong>End of March 2021 <\/strong>(the exact date was agreed with the participants)<\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator is-style-default\"\/>\n\n\n\n<h4>Public User Profiles<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>GoTriple&#8217;s registered users will have a public profile page where all the relevant information is publicly available to other users browsing the platform. Workshop participants help us design this page, defining what is important to display and how to display all the relevant information.<br>This workshop was held by Giulio Andreini of Net7 Srl.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\ud83d\uddd3 Date: <strong>Wednesday 24th March 2021, from 10.00 to 12.00 CET<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n<\/div>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>List of Upcoming WorkshopsList of Past Workshops Participate in the Co-Design Workshops and help us shape the GoTriple platform! Our team is planning some co-design workshops where potential users of the platform will be directly and actively involved in the<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":7,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/706"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/7"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=706"}],"version-history":[{"count":63,"href":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/706\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":2475,"href":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/706\/revisions\/2475"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=706"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}